short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bring the hero-in-the-making Izuku Midoriya from My Hero Academia to your browser with this inspiring Chrome extension.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Featuring a live wallpaper of Midoriya, this extension showcases his determination, growth, and unwavering courage. Every new tab will remind you of his journey to becoming the number one hero.

Features:
🎨 High-quality live wallpaper of Izuku Midoriya from My Hero Academia.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display for a practical and stylish browsing experience.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts to your favorite websites.
Let Izuku Midoriya’s heroic spirit motivate you as you browse the web, with each new tab filled with the promise of growth and adventure. Perfect for My Hero Academia fans and those who admire Midoriya’s relentless pursuit of justice.
